---
title: Crumbed Chicken Tenders & Beetroot Relish with Kumara Fries & Cherry Tomato Garden Salad
description: Spiced all nice and crumbed to golden perfection, it would be a crime to deprive these juicy chicken tenders of a good
dipping sauce. Lucky we’ve got two - a tangy relish and creamy mayo pairing. Don’t forget to dip in the kumara fries too!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
